/uploads/2022/01/Martin-Shkreli-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Martin-Shkreli-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>马丁·什克雷利 (Martin Shkreli) 被勒令交出他的罕见<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">武当派</a>专辑《少林往事》(Once Upon A Time In Shaolin)。</p><p>据<a href="https://news.artnet.com/art-world/martin-shkreli-wu-tang-clan-album-copying-ruling-2527688"><em>ArtNet</em></a>报道，一名法官命令 Skhreli 在一周内推翻他拥有的所有副本，并于周五上午（8 月 23 日）通过了裁决。该判决<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkreli-sued-for-copying-and-playing-wu-tang-clans-once-upon-a-time-in-shaolin-without-permission-3765468">源于数字艺术团体 PleasrDAO 在 6 月份起诉 Shkreli 未经许可复制和播放该专辑</a>。</p><p>法官帕梅拉·陈还要求什克莱里提供一份宣誓书，确认他的放弃，以及他制作的所有副本的清单、他分发给谁，以及从分发中获得的任何利润。 Shkreli 已被命令在 30 天内将清单提供给法官。</p><p>史莱克利的律师没有立即回应<em>ArtNet</em>的置评请求。 </p><figure id="attachment_2738464" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2738464" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2738464" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482.jpg" alt="马丁·施克莱利" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2738464" class="wp-caption-text">马丁·什克雷利 (Martin Shkreli) 图片来源：Drew Angerer/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这位前对冲基金经理和“制药兄弟” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rza-regrets-selling-wu-tang-clans-once-upon-a-time-in-shaolin-martin-shkreli-album-3081934">于 205 年以 200 万美元（140 万英镑）购买了该唱片的唯一副本</a>，去年 6 月因非法直播该专辑而被起诉。</p><p> Shkreli 购买了这张专辑，条件是这张专辑在 2103 年之前不能用于商业用途，尽管它可以在聆听聚会上播放。尽管有限制，他还是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkreli-plays-fabled-wu-tang-album-as-he-discusses-fraud-conviction-2122235">在 2017 年的直播中播放了专辑的片段</a>，然后尝试在 eBay 上出售这张专辑。</p><p>尽管出售从未完成，但施克莱利因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/martin-shkreli-found-guilty-fraud-2121196">证券欺诈被定罪</a>后被迫交出专辑，联邦法院扣押了价值 740 万美元（580 万英镑）的资产。该专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkrelis-2million-wu-tang-clan-album-has-been-sold-by-the-us-government-3004668">现由数字艺术团体 PleasrDAO 持有。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkreli-ordered-to-surrender-his-copies-of-rare-wu-tang-clan-album-3787005">马丁·施克莱利 (Martin Shkreli) 下令交出他的罕见武当派专辑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
