/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_RENEERAPP-621388-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_RENEERAPP-621388-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_RENEERAPP-621388-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">蕾妮·拉普 (Reneé Rapp</a> ) 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁 2024</a>主舞台今天（8 月 25 日）因技术困难和水落在她身上而被缩短。</p><p>这位明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-2024-renee-rapp-pulls-out-of-leeds-main-stage-3786316">在周五（8 月 23 日）利兹的演出因极端天气而被取消，</a>这是她在音乐节上的首次亮相。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3785825">Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 直播博客：所有发生的动作</a></strong></li></ul><p>拉普的雷丁现场立刻就出现了问题，这位歌手上台时麦克风坏了。问题解决后，她离开了舞台，等待的人群高喊着她的名字。 “良好的错误开始！”回来后她笑了，并以《Talk Too Much》和《Poison Poison》拉开了演出的序幕。</p><p>在第三首歌《Bruises》中，昨天下雨时聚集在舞台顶部的水被强风吹到了舞台上。拉普和她乐队的设备和乐器被突如其来的倾盆大雨浸湿，迫使她再次离开舞台。 “哦，你们这些英国婊子！”她走开时喊道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_GX8HSJSLF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex